      "created": 1776798421,
      "updated": 1776798421
    },
    {
      "id": "69e7cae200000000009884f1",
      "text": "[suto3.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776798434,
      "updated": 1776798445
    },
    {
      "id": "69e7caea00000000009884f2",
      "text": " 昨日のあれで少しだけ[承認欲求]が満たされた",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776798443,
      "updated": 1776798537
    },
    {
      "id": "69e7cb0700000000009884f3",
      "text": " 井戸端で書きたい欲が蓄積されるイベント",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776798472,
      "updated": 1776801820
    },
    {
      "id": "69e7ce1b0000000000f8003f",
      "text": " 見る人は見ている",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776799259,
      "updated": 1776799275
    },
    {
      "id": "69e7cdf00000000000f8003e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776799216,
      "updated": 1776799216
    },
    {
      "id": "69e83654000000000009dcb2",
      "text": " whoさんはなぁ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776825941,
      "updated": 1776825964
    },
    {
      "id": "69e8366e000000000009dcb4",
      "text": "  who1 - who4 で特に困ったことはないしなあ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776825966,
      "updated": 1776826038
    },
    {
      "id": "69e836b8000000000009dcb5",
      "text": "  who5（ふーこ）のピクトグラム版も使われないで、キャラの画像固定になっているしなあ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776826041,
      "updated": 1776826315
    },
    {
      "id": "69e83728000000000009dcb6",
      "text": "  [ミープルくん] [meeple1.icon][meeple2.icon][meeple3.icon][meeple4.icon]とか作ったんだが、誰も使ってくれない",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776826153,
      "updated": 1776828356
    },
    {
      "id": "69e83657000000000009dcb3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776825944,
      "updated": 1776825944
    },
    {
      "id": "69e842470000000000f2c6df",
      "text": " [dummy_member]増えすぎ問題",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776829000,
      "updated": 1776829041
    },
    {
      "id": "69e8423d0000000000f2c6dd",
      "text": "　 [会話形式コンテンツのキャラクター紹介（非実在編）]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776828989,
      "updated": 1776829044
    },
    {
      "id": "69e842aa0000000000f2c6e0",
      "text": "　 一発芸みたいにキャラを量産してもねえ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776829098,
      "updated": 1776829138
    },
    {
      "id": "69e842d20000000000f2c6e1",
      "text": "　 　ほとんど使われないキャラが多い",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776829138,
      "updated": 1776829169
    },
    {
      "id": "69e8423e0000000000f2c6de",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776828991,
      "updated": 1776828991
    },
    {
      "id": "69e848010000000000f2c6e2",
      "text": "　[太宰]のページはあっても[太宰治]のページはない。この現象を何と言う？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776830465,
      "updated": 1776830544
    },
    {
      "id": "69e8497f000000000009dcc8",
      "text": "　 太宰治、おそらく自分より詳しい人が多くいるので、ページをつくるの躊躇している",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776830848,
      "updated": 1776830950
    },
    {
      "id": "69e849f8000000000009dcc9",
      "text": "　  文豪三大クズの話とかしたら、たぶん怒られる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776830968,
      "updated": 1776846245
    },
    {
      "id": "69e848020000000000f2c6e3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776830467,
      "updated": 1776830467
    },
    {
      "id": "69e87deb000000000043a26e",
      "text": " [Font Awesome]と[icongram]でuserのアイコンが違うのか、これはおそらくicongramのフォントが古いせい",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776844269,
      "updated": 1776844479
    },
    {
      "id": "69e87ed4000000000043a270",
      "text": " 　Font Awesomeのアイコンを採用しよう",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776844500,
      "updated": 1776844553
    },
    {
      "id": "69e87ef7000000000043a271",
      "text": " 　　時間をかければ、icongramのsvgも見つかるだろうけど、そこまでする意味はないだろう",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776844535,
      "updated": 1776844675
    },
    {
      "id": "69e87ded000000000043a26f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776844269,
      "updated": 1776844269
    },
    {
      "id": "69e882b80000000000307c86",
      "text": " まったくの余談ですが、[suto3.icon]開始の色を赤から青に変更しました",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776845497,
      "updated": 1776845568
    },
    {
      "id": "69e883000000000000307c88",
      "text": " 　すこしだけ落ち着いた感じになったと思います",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776845568,
      "updated": 1776845599
    },
    {
      "id": "69e882b90000000000307c87",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776845498,
      "updated": 1776845498
    },
    {
      "id": "69e8bac60000000000afc2d8",
      "text": "　人はなぜ、過去の失敗事例に学ばないのか",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776859846,
      "updated": 1776859894
    },
    {
      "id": "69e8baf60000000000afc2da",
      "text": "　　これは、自分にも言える。後で反省しよう",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776859894,
      "updated": 1776859941
    },
    {
      "id": "69e8f5b20000000000776cc4",
      "text": "　　　議論のハンドリングが下手",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776874930,
      "updated": 1776874956
    },
    {
      "id": "69e8bac70000000000afc2d9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776859848,
      "updated": 1776859848
    },
    {
      "id": "69e8bdf20000000000afc2db",
      "text": " 2chまとめブログのテキスト切り貼り問題というのがあった",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776860658,
      "updated": 1776860716
    },
    {
      "id": "69e8be2c0000000000afc2dd",
      "text": " 　話を面白くするために、恣意的な編集をして、元の発言者の意見を捻じ曲げた",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776860716,
      "updated": 1776861061
    },
    {
      "id": "69e8bec30000000000afc2de",
      "text": " 　評判が悪かった",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776860867,
      "updated": 1776860881
    },
    {
      "id": "69e8bdf70000000000afc2dc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776860663,
      "updated": 1776860663
    }
  ]
